# SDK 56+ makes expo/fetch the default global fetch implementation. This
# app's entire API layer (src/lib/mealieApi.ts) — including the 3 multipart
# uploads (recipe image, attachments, AI image-to-recipe) that use the
# classic RN `{ uri, name, type }` FormData part pattern — was built and
# tested against React Native's built-in fetch, which multiple confirmed
# reports (expo/expo#33134) show expo/fetch does NOT support for that
# pattern ("Unsupported FormDataPart implementation"). Keeping RN's fetch
# global avoids that regression entirely rather than migrating 3 call sites
# to a newer, still-churning expo-file-system File API this app has no
# other need for.
EXPO_PUBLIC_USE_RN_FETCH=1
